{"title":"CentSO 7.4 下安装jdk1.8、mysql、php服务","date":"2018-04-22T22:51:00.000Z","link":"post/43","tags":["1.8.0","gcj","grep","java","javarpm","jdkrpm","mysql","open-jdk","php","php-fpm","service","yum","命令","安装","文件","系统"],"categories":["Liunx"],"updated":"2019-04-27T13:33:07.780Z","content":"<h1 id=\"1-安装jdk1-8\">1.安装jdk1.8<a href=\"post/43#1-安装jdk1-8\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"1-1-安装之前先检查一下系统有没有自带open-jdk1-1-安装之前先检查一下系统有没有自带open-jdk\">1.1 安装之前先检查一下系统有没有自带open-jdk1.1 安装之前先检查一下系统有没有自带open-jdk<a href=\"post/43#1-1-安装之前先检查一下系统有没有自带open-jdk1-1-安装之前先检查一下系统有没有自带open-jdk\"></a></h2><p>命令：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">rpm -qa |grep java</span><br><span class=\"line\">rpm -qa |grep jdk</span><br><span class=\"line\">rpm -qa |grep gcj</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p>如果没有输入信息表示没有安装。<br>如果安装可以使用如果安装可以使用<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">rpm -qa | grep java | xargs rpm -e --nodeps</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p>批量卸载所有带有Java的文件  这句命令的关键字是java</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-2-检索包含java的列表\">1.2 检索包含java的列表<a href=\"post/43#1-2-检索包含java的列表\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum list java*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h2 id=\"1-3-检索1-8的列表\">1.3 检索1.8的列表<a href=\"post/43#1-3-检索1-8的列表\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum list java-1.8*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"1-4-安装1-8-0的所有文件\">1.4 安装1.8.0的所有文件<a href=\"post/43#1-4-安装1-8-0的所有文件\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum install java-1.8.0-openjdk* -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"1-5-使用命令检查是否安装成功\">1.5 使用命令检查是否安装成功<a href=\"post/43#1-5-使用命令检查是否安装成功\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">java -version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h1 id=\"2-安装mysql、php、httpd服务\">2.安装mysql、php、httpd服务<a href=\"post/43#2-安装mysql、php、httpd服务\"></a></h1><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum install -y httpd php php-fpm mysql mysql-server php-mysql</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"2-1-服务启动\">2.1 服务启动<a href=\"post/43#2-1-服务启动\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">service httpd start  </span><br><span class=\"line\">service mysqld start  </span><br><span class=\"line\">service php-fpm start</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"2-2-查看状态\">2.2 查看状态<a href=\"post/43#2-2-查看状态\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">netstat -tunlp</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>","prev":{"title":"在本地用navicat链接不上阿里云ECS服务器上的数据库问题解决","link":"post/44"},"next":{"title":"阿里云服务器下(centOS)中安装ftp","link":"post/40"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/43/","toc":[{"title":"1.安装jdk1.8","id":"1-安装jdk1-8","index":"1","children":[{"title":"1.1 安装之前先检查一下系统有没有自带open-jdk1.1 安装之前先检查一下系统有没有自带open-jdk","id":"1-1-安装之前先检查一下系统有没有自带open-jdk1-1-安装之前先检查一下系统有没有自带open-jdk","index":"1.1"},{"title":"1.2 检索包含java的列表","id":"1-2-检索包含java的列表","index":"1.2"},{"title":"1.3 检索1.8的列表","id":"1-3-检索1-8的列表","index":"1.3"},{"title":"1.4 安装1.8.0的所有文件","id":"1-4-安装1-8-0的所有文件","index":"1.4"},{"title":"1.5 使用命令检查是否安装成功","id":"1-5-使用命令检查是否安装成功","index":"1.5"}]},{"title":"2.安装mysql、php、httpd服务","id":"2-安装mysql、php、httpd服务","index":"2","children":[{"title":"2.1 服务启动","id":"2-1-服务启动","index":"2.1"},{"title":"2.2 查看状态","id":"2-2-查看状态","index":"2.2"}]}]}